       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CARDDB2.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-CARD-NO PIC X(16).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE CARDACCT END-EXEC.
